    <h3>Community Information</h3>
    <p>Tacoma is located at the foot of Mount Rainier and along the shores of Commencement Bay in Washington State. Tacoma is recognized as a livable and progressive international city. Tacoma is a thriving city with a revitalized downtown that caters to residents and visitors alike with its shopping, dining, theaters and award-winning arts and architecture. Tacoma offers world-class museums, beautiful parks, and a scenic waterfront. You can enjoy all the outdoor beauty that Tacoma has to offer and while visiting many of these popular Tacoma attractions.</p>
