    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>The Tacoma Public Schools is the third largest district in Washington State. The district has been a "lighthouse" district for many years and often leads the way for the state's 296 districts in piloting new programs and implementing innovative ideas. The vision for Tacoma is to be an outstanding school district in which all students exhibit high standards of achievement and critical thinking skills, and are socially responsible, contributing members of their community. Deep, sustainable partnerships are formed with students, parents, and community members so students have additional support in order to reach these high standards.</p>
